<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hip1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hip,</orth> the joint of the thigh with the flesh covering it, the haunch: <bibl n="shak. ven 44" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 113</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.2.47" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 2, 47</bibl>. <emph>to catch</emph> or <emph>have on the h.</emph> == to lay or have hold of, to have at advantage: <bibl n="shak. mv 1.3.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 3, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.334" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 334</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.314" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 314</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>